snippet.title: Hellpit - Level Flythrough
snippet.description:
I made a flythrough on the first level, showcasing many traps and platforms you have to overcome.
But take note, video  only show first level, there's more level 
with even more unique traps/platforms.

Hellpit is coming out on steam on 9 January 2023
Wishlist now
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2094390/HELLPIT/

Music by:
ILLUSION by Aim To Head
